<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etlich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, den der edel <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Eberh<ex>art,</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> zu Eppenstein, ettwievil
                            <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab und
                            <expan>kawffmansch<ex>aft</ex></expan> nehst
                            <expan>aufgehalt<ex>en</ex></expan> hett, wol fürbracht und gesagt, wie
                        ir in und den iren in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gar hilfflich und
                            <expan>furderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> seyt und ewch ser
                            <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> gemüet habt, daz in und den iren gar
                        ausztregenlich <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> und zu
                            <expan>gute<ex>m</ex></expan> nucz <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey,
                        des <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleiss und begern das umb ewch und die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> zu
                        verdienen. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> oculi. </ab>
</div>
